" Remap Caps lock
imap <C-a> <Esc>
vmap <C-a> <Esc>

" Case-insensitive searching.
set ignorecase

" But case-sensitive if expression contains a capital letter.
set smartcase

" Default to global substitutions on lines
set gdefault

" Move between assistant editors
nnoremap <C-j> <C-w>j
nnoremap <C-k> <C-w>k
nnoremap <C-l> <C-w>l
nnoremap <C-h> <C-w>h

" Comment & uncomment
nnoremap \c :xccmd commentAndUncommentCurrentLines<CR>
vnoremap \c :xccmd commentAndUncommentCurrentLines<CR>

" Indent selection
nnoremap \i ==

" Open navigator
nnoremap \n :xccmd toggleNavigatorsVisibility<CR>
